summary: Y’know, for a blog that basically does nothing but lovingly talk shit about Dan and Phil, and their fans, I don’t get nearly as...
body:
Y’know, for a blog that basically does nothing but lovingly talk shit about Dan and Phil, and their fans, I don’t get nearly as much hate as one would expect.


Thank y’all for being rational sons of bitches.


(But also like, don’t be scared to send me opinions that conflict with my own. This ain’t no echo chamber)
